answers.body_markdown:
Firstly: 

    IOSDriver driver = new IOSDriver(url, capabilities); 
    driver.manage().timeouts().implicitlyWait(10, TimeUnit.SECONDS);
is enough to launch your application, no need to call `driver.launchApp();`

Secondly: try use `capabilities.setCapability(&quot;fullReset&quot;, true);` instead of `capabilities.setCapability(MobileCapabilityType.NO_RESET, true);`

